        create:     "Construct a fully annotated nitrogen cycle diagram for a waterlogged river floodplain that is periodically flooded in winter and exposed in summer. Your diagram must: (a) show all major nitrogen transformations with named bacteria or processes; (b) annotate which transformations are enhanced during winter flooding and which are enhanced during summer exposure; (c) show the direction of net nitrogen flux in and out of the ecosystem; (d) identify where in the cycle greenhouse gas emissions (N₂O, NH₃) occur; (e) propose one management intervention that would reduce N₂O emissions from this system."
