        create:     "Propose a comprehensive management plan for a neonate diagnosed with X-linked SCID via TREC-positive newborn screening, before any infections have occurred. Your plan must address: (a) immediate protective measures and contraindicated interventions (specify which and explain why); (b) investigation to confirm diagnosis and determine HLA matching status; (c) decision between HSCT and gene therapy with justification; (d) monitoring parameters for immune reconstitution; (e) long-term follow-up and what complications to monitor for."
